{"tid":1405445,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"MTR遊車河交流","createTime":"2019-08-04T09:42:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T12:40:09.000Z","uid":107681,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9dc45c92cd497e65eeda0c3f36f6b8adc4e61e3a","tid":1405445,"uid":107681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:42:44.000Z","msg":"有部份鐵路愛好者唔敢試下緊急制同玩門，而想遊下車河觀光下，但坐足全程又長又浪費時間，不如集中某幾個站不停來回享受。<br />\n例如觀塘線往黃埔方向，其實一到太子就大量人落車轉車，之後幾個站大把位根本唔會爆，坐到總站又冇野好睇浪費時間，不如不停來回彩虹or鑽石山至石峽尾成效更大。<br />\n理論最多野睇應該係來回樂富至石峽尾，但由於樂富極難上車，所以建議不如去到彩虹鑽石山易上車遊多幾班車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有緊急需要使用緊急制既乘客，記得盡量係部車未開或入左站先按，如果係部車未入到一半or開到一半按，職員要檢查好耐先開得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"587def99ab1899c8e1c88e73caa0f500e85ad9b5","tid":1405445,"uid":107681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:06:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f6c772ef9aa0217c7716e5e3d060e7084d751cc","tid":1405445,"uid":107681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:06:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f84a5c6026e4ce4307f16f822556a8823d7e2431","tid":1405445,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:07:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1405338/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1405338/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[804] 係堅尼地城/西環有需要落腳嘅手足入黎!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ca1b5276c3a3c2085807eab24e497e7a5432143","tid":1405445,"uid":219277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:09:24.000Z","msg":"朝早五點<br />\n有車揸車<br />\n無車塞鐵"},{"pid":"db08cde2b